item.title: About me
item.description:
I’m 30 and I live in Natal (RN - Brazil). I’ve been coding, since 2006, in many different languages, like Delphi, Java, Ruby, Javascript and Go

I did a lot of Ruby code in the last five years and for the last two years, I’m doing a lot of Go code to create fast and reliable products.
